source_text: Vakatikitikitaki e vale me 14 na siga.
target_text: Self-isolate for 14 full days.

source_text: E dodonu mo vakatikitikitaki mai na siga e vakilai kina na tauvimate vei koya e liu ena nomu matavuvale.
target_text: You need to self-isolate from the day the first person in your household started symptoms.

source_text: Kevaka e sega ni laurai na ivakatakilakila, vakatikitikitaki iko mai na siga e caka kina na veivakatovotovo.
target_text: If they have no symptoms, self-isolate from the day of their test.

source_text: Na ibalebale ni vakatikitikitaki e vale: mo tiko ga e vale ka kakua ni lako icakacaka, vuli se na vanua era sota kina vakalewelevu na lewenivanua.
target_text: Self-isolate means stay home and do not go to work, school, or public areas.

source_text: Kakua ni vakayagataka na tolili ni lewenivanua se na taxi.
target_text: Do not use public transport or taxis.

source_text: Kevaka o vakila na taqa ni icegu, qarai vakatotolo na veivuke vakavuniwai.
target_text: If you experience difficulty breathing, seek immediate medical attention.

source_text: Na mosi ni sarisari e sega ni cegu rawa e dua na ivakatakilakila bibi.
target_text: Persistent chest pain is a warning sign.

source_text: Na veilecayaki ni vakasama se dredre me yadra vakabalavu e gadreva na veivuke vakatotolo.
target_text: New confusion or inability to stay awake requires urgent care.

source_text: O ira na sivia na 50 na yabaki se tauvi mate vakadua me ra gole ki na screening clinic.
target_text: Anyone over 50 or with chronic illness should visit a screening clinic.

source_text: Dementia e vakamacalataka na ivakatakilakila ena veisau e yaco ena ivakarau ni cakacaka ni mona.
target_text: Dementia describes symptoms caused by changes in how the brain works.

source_text: Na mate na Alzheimers e mataqali dementia e dau kunei vakalevu.
target_text: Alzheimer's disease is the most common type of dementia.

source_text: E rawa ni dua ga e tauvi dementia, ia e tubu na kena loloma ni sa qase na tamata.
target_text: Anyone can get dementia, but the chance increases with age.

source_text: E dau dredre me kilai na ivakatakilakila taumada ni dementia.
target_text: Early signs of dementia can be difficult to notice.

source_text: E levu na mate e rawa ni qaravi ka vakavuna na ivakatakilakila e vaka na dementia.
target_text: Many treatable illnesses can cause dementia-like symptoms.

source_text: Raica vakatotolo na nomu vuniwai kevaka o lomaleqataka.
target_text: See your doctor if you are worried.

source_text: Na guiguileca vou e vakaleqa na bula wasoma.
target_text: Recent memory loss that affects daily life.

source_text: Na dredre ni cakava na itavi e kilai tu vakawasoma.
target_text: Difficulty performing familiar tasks.

source_text: Na leqa ena vosa.
target_text: Problems with language.

source_text: Na lutusobu ni vakatulewa se vakasama cala.
target_text: Poor judgment or decision-making.

source_text: Na vascular dementia e vakavuna na sega ni veirauti vinaka na dra e drodro ki na mona.
target_text: Vascular dementia is caused by poor blood supply to the brain.

source_text: E rauta ni dua mai na lewe tolu vei ira na tauvi Alzheimers e tiko na wekadra voleka e tauvi dementia.
target_text: A third of people with Alzheimer's have a close relative with dementia.

source_text: Na dementia e sega ni dau tubu ga ena kawa.
target_text: Dementia is not always inherited.

source_text: Kevaka o kila ni tauvi iko na dementia, e sa tu na veivuke vei iko.
target_text: If you find out you have dementia, help is available.

source_text: E rawa ni ko rawata na itukutuku, wainimate kei na veitokoni.
target_text: You can get information, medication, and support.

source_text: Na ivakatakilakila ni COVID-19 e oka kina na vuvu, katakata, savu ni ucu, wadadamu na mata, kei na sega ni vakila na ikanakana se boica.
target_text: COVID-19 symptoms include cough, fever, runny nose, red eyes, and loss of taste or smell.

source_text: Kevaka o vakila ni leka nomu icegu, gole vakatotolo ki na vale ni bula voleka duadua.
target_text: If you have difficulty breathing, go immediately to a health facility.

source_text: E levu na tamata ena rawa ni bula vinaka ga e vale ka sega ni gadreva na qaravi vakavuniwai.
target_text: Most people will recover at home without medical intervention.

source_text: O ira na tamata cakacaka e vakila na ivakatakilakila era rawa ni taura na ivola ni 14 na siga ni tiko vakatikitiki e vale.
target_text: Workers with symptoms can get a medical certificate for 14 days of self-isolation.

source_text: Na veivakatovotovo e vukea na kena kilai o ira era beci vakalevu ni rawa ni tauvi mate bibi.
target_text: Testing helps identify people at risk of severe illness.

source_text: Na screening clinic e vakatabakidua vei ira era tiko ena iwasewase ni rerevaki vakalevu.
target_text: Screening clinics focus on high-risk groups.

source_text: Na tiko vakatikitiki e vale e tarova na kena vakatetei na COVID-19 vei ira na tani.
target_text: Self-isolation helps prevent the spread of COVID-19 to others.

source_text: O Mika e imatai ni tauvimate ni COVID-19 ena nona matavuvale.
target_text: Mika is the first case of COVID-19 in this household.

source_text: Na siga e laurai kina vei Mika na ivakatakilakila era sa tekivu tiko vakatikitiki kina na lewe ni matavuvale taucoko.
target_text: Everyone in the household starts self-isolating on the day Mika's symptoms start.

source_text: O ira na lewe ni matavuvale e tiko ena iwasewase ni rerevaki vakalevu me ra gole ki na screening clinic mera qai vakatovotovotaki kina.
target_text: High-risk family members should visit a screening clinic and get tested.

source_text: Cava na tiko vakatikitiki kevaka sa oti na 14 na siga ka sega ni laurai e dua na ivakatakilakila me 3 na siga sa sivi.
target_text: Stop isolating if you have completed 14 days and had no symptoms for at least 3 days.

source_text: E duidui na kena vakilai na dementia vei ira na tamata yadua.
target_text: Dementia is different for everyone.

source_text: Na ivakatakilakila e qai ca vakamalua ni sa levu na veisau ena mona.
target_text: Symptoms get worse as brain changes increase.

source_text: Na nomu kila taumada ni tauvi iko na dementia e kena ibalebale ni rawa ni vukei iko vakatotolo na kenadau.
target_text: Finding out early that you have dementia means you can get help sooner.

source_text: Na guiguileca duadua e sega ni kena ibalebale ni sa tauvi iko na dementia.
target_text: Memory lapses alone do not mean you have dementia.

source_text: Na veisau ena ivakarau ni yalo kei na itovo e rawa ni ivakatakilakila ni dementia.
target_text: Changes in mood and behaviour can be a sign of dementia.

source_text: E tubucake na protein vakatubu mate ena mona ena mate na Alzheimers.
target_text: Abnormal proteins build up in the brain in Alzheimer's disease.

source_text: Na ivakatakilakila ni vascular dementia e rawa ni tekivu vakasauri ni oti e dua na stroke.
target_text: The symptoms of vascular dementia can start suddenly after a stroke.

source_text: Kevaka ko leqataka na isema ni vuvale kei na dementia, vosa vua na nomu vuniwai.
target_text: For concerns about a family history of dementia, talk to your doctor.

source_text: Na veika e rawa ni qaravi e rawa ni vakavuna na sega ni nanuma, veilecayaki kei na guiguileca.
target_text: Treatable conditions can cause memory lapses, confusion, and forgetfulness.

source_text: Kevaka ko leqataka ni rawa ni tauvi iko se dua ko kila na dementia, vosa vua na nomu vuniwai se vakailesilesi ni tabana ni bula.
target_text: If you are worried that you or someone you know may have dementia, talk to your healthcare provider.

source_text: E tu e Alzheimers New Zealand e vuqa na itukutuku me baleta na dementia.
target_text: Alzheimers New Zealand has many resources about dementia.

source_text: Na itukutuku oqori e rawa ni sauma e vuqa na taro e tiko vei iko.
target_text: These resources can answer many questions you may have.

source_text: Na ivola About Dementia e dua na idusidusi vei ira era sa kilai ni tauvi ira na dementia.
target_text: The booklet About Dementia is a guide for people diagnosed with dementia.

source_text: Na ivola e vakamacalataka na ivakatakilakila taumada kei na kena vakadeitaki na dementia.
target_text: The booklet explains early warning signs and diagnosis of dementia.

source_text: E vakamacalataki talega ena ivola na bulabula ni mona kei na kena vakalailaitaki na vakatarausui ni mate.
target_text: The booklet covers brain health and risk reduction.

source_text: Na ivola e vakaraitaka na mataqali veitokoni e sa tu.
target_text: The booklet explains what support is available.

source_text: Na ivola e uqeta na kena caka na ituvatuva me baleta na veigauna mai muri.
target_text: The booklet encourages future planning.

source_text: Na veivakatovotovo ni COVID-19 e vakatabakidua vei ira era tiko ena iwasewase ni rawa ni tauvi mate bibi.
target_text: COVID-19 testing is targeted to people at high risk of severe illness.

source_text: Na veivakatovotovo e vukea na kena kilai ka qaravi o ira era beci vakalevu ni rawa ni tauvi COVID-19 bibi.
target_text: Testing helps identify and treat people at risk of severe COVID-19.

source_text: Kevaka o sivia na 50 na yabaki ka vakila na ivakatakilakila lailai ni COVID-19, o dodonu mo gole ki na screening clinic.
target_text: If you have mild COVID-19 symptoms and are over 50, you should visit a screening clinic.

source_text: Kevaka o tauvi mate ni suka, mate ni uto, mate ni ivi, dau cegu oca se levulevu sivia, o tiko ena iwasewase ni rerevaki vakalevu.
target_text: If you have diabetes, heart disease, kidney disease, asthma, or are obese, you are at higher risk.

source_text: O ira na bukete tiko ka vakila na ivakatakilakila ni COVID-19 me ra vakatovotovotaki.
target_text: Pregnant people with COVID-19 symptoms should be tested.

source_text: Kevaka e vakadeitaki ni sa tauvi iko na COVID-19, ena qaravi iko vakatotolo na timi ni Tabana ni Bula.
target_text: If you test positive, health teams will provide immediate care.

source_text: Kevaka e lailai ga na ivakatakilakila ka sega ni tiko ena iwasewase ni rerevaki vakalevu, e rawa ni sega ni gadrevi na veivakatovotovo.
target_text: If you have mild symptoms and are not high risk, you may not need a test.

source_text: E levu era tauvi COVID-19 lailai era na bula vinaka taucoko ga e vale.
target_text: Most people with mild COVID-19 will fully recover at home.

source_text: Kevaka o vakila na ivakatakilakila ni COVID-19, o dodonu mo vakayawaki iko mai vei ira na nomu lewe ni matavuvale.
target_text: You should isolate from your family members if you have COVID-19 symptoms.

source_text: Ni o tiko e vale, vakaraica vakavinaka nodrau veisau na nomu ivakatakilakila.
target_text: Monitor your symptoms closely while you are at home.

source_text: Kevaka sa bibi na ivakatakilakila, gole vakatotolo ki na vale ni bula e qarava vakatabakidua na COVID-19.
target_text: If your symptoms become severe, go immediately to a dedicated health facility.

source_text: O ira na tamata cakacaka e vakila na ivakatakilakila era rawa ni gole ki na screening clinic mera taura kina na ivola ni tauvimate.
target_text: Workers with symptoms can attend a screening clinic to obtain a medical certificate.

source_text: Na ivola ni tauvimate e rawa ni solia na 14 na siga ni tiko vakatikitiki e vale.
target_text: A medical certificate can provide 14 days of self-isolation at home.

source_text: Na vuniwai taucoko era sa vakadonuya na matanitu e rawa tale ga ni solia na ivola ni tiko vakatikitiki e vale.
target_text: Private doctors approved by the Ministry can also provide medical certificates for self-isolation.

source_text: Kevaka o tauvi mate ni suka, o tiko ena iwasewase ni rerevaki vakalevu ni COVID-19.
target_text: If you have diabetes, you are at higher risk of severe COVID-19.

source_text: Kevaka o tauvi mate ni suka ka vakila na ivakatakilakila ni COVID-19, gole vakatotolo ki na screening clinic.
target_text: If you have diabetes and COVID-19 symptoms, visit a screening clinic immediately.

source_text: Ira era tauvi mate ni suka me ra vakaraica vakavinaka na nodrau ivakatakilakila ni COVID-19.
target_text: People with diabetes should monitor their symptoms closely during COVID-19.

source_text: Kevaka o tauvi mate ni uto, o tiko ena iwasewase ni rerevaki vakalevu ni COVID-19.
target_text: If you have heart disease, you are at higher risk of severe COVID-19.

source_text: Kevaka o tauvi mate ni uto ka vakila na ivakatakilakila ni COVID-19, gole vakatotolo ki na screening clinic.

target_text: People over 50 years of age are at higher risk of severe COVID-19.

source_text: Anxiety is a normal human emotion that can feel like changing waves on the ocean.
target_text: Na loma taqaya e dua nai vakarau vakayalo e dau yaco vakawasoma ka rawa ni vaka na veisau ni ua ni wasawasa.

source_text: Na loma taqaya e dua nai vakarau vakayalo e dau yaco vakawasoma ka rawa ni vaka na veisau ni ua ni wasawasa.
target_text: Anxiety is a normal human emotion that can feel like changing waves on the ocean.

source_text: Anxiety can be described as worry, feeling nervous or feeling uneasy about something.
target_text: Na loma taqaya e rawa ni vakamacalataki me vaka na lomaleqa, nuiqawaqawa se nanuma dredre e dua na ka.

source_text: Na loma taqaya e rawa ni vakamacalataki me vaka na lomaleqa, nuiqawaqawa se nanuma dredre e dua na ka.
target_text: Anxiety can be described as worry, feeling nervous or feeling uneasy about something.

source_text: Many people feel anxious when they face new or unknown situations.
target_text: E levu na tamata era dau loma taqaya ni ra sotava na veika vou se veika era sega ni dau kila.

source_text: E levu na tamata era dau loma taqaya ni ra sotava na veika vou se veika era sega ni dau kila.
target_text: Many people feel anxious when they face new or unknown situations.

source_text: Sometimes anxiety is helpful because it makes us alert and motivated.
target_text: E so na gauna na loma taqaya e dau veivuke ni sa vakayadrati keda ka vakauqeti keda.

source_text: E so na gauna na loma taqaya e dau veivuke ni sa vakayadrati keda ka vakauqeti keda.
target_text: Sometimes anxiety is helpful because it makes us alert and motivated.

source_text: Unhelpful anxiety makes us feel stuck and blinds us to our own strengths.
target_text: Na loma taqaya e sega ni veivuke e vakavuna meda taroga tu ka meda sega ni raica na noda kaukauwa vakataki keda.

source_text: Na loma taqaya e sega ni veivuke e vakavuna meda taroga tu ka meda sega ni raica na noda kaukauwa vakataki keda.
target_text: Unhelpful anxiety makes us feel stuck and blinds us to our own strengths.

source_text: Our heart may beat faster and our chest can feel tight when we are anxious.
target_text: Ni da loma taqaya e rawa ni totolo na vadugu ni uto ka tadre na sereda.

source_text: Ni da loma taqaya e rawa ni totolo na vadugu ni uto ka tadre na sereda.
target_text: Our heart may beat faster and our chest can feel tight when we are anxious.

source_text: We may feel sick in the stomach, get headaches or feel dizzy.
target_text: E rawa ni da lomaloma ca, mosi na ulu se vakila na matabuto.

source_text: E rawa ni da lomaloma ca, mosi na ulu se vakila na matabuto.
target_text: We may feel sick in the stomach, get headaches or feel dizzy.

source_text: We might have trouble concentrating and staying focused.
target_text: E rawa ni dredre meda vakasamataka vinaka na veika ka sega ni rawarawa meda vakabibitaka e dua na ka.

source_text: E rawa ni dredre meda vakasamataka vinaka na veika ka sega ni rawarawa meda vakabibitaka e dua na ka.
target_text: We might have trouble concentrating and staying focused.

source_text: We may start avoiding places or situations that make us feel anxious.
target_text: E rawa ni da tekivu levea na veivanua se veika eda vakila ni vakavuna na loma taqaya.

target_text: We may start avoiding places or situations that make us feel anxious.

source_text: We may feel disconnected spiritually and lose our sense of peace.
target_text: E rawa ni da vakila ni da yawa vakayalo ka yali na noda yalo vakacegu.

source_text: E rawa ni da vakila ni da yawa vakayalo ka yali na noda yalo vakacegu.
target_text: We may feel disconnected spiritually and lose our sense of peace.

source_text: Depression is more than feeling sad, stressed or angry for a short time.
target_text: Na lomabibi e sivia ga na yalorarawa, lomaocaoca se cudru ena loma ni dua na gauna lekaleka.

source_text: Na lomabibi e sivia ga na yalorarawa, lomaocaoca se cudru ena loma ni dua na gauna lekaleka.
target_text: Depression is more than feeling sad, stressed or angry for a short time.

source_text: Depression is feeling stuck with heavy emotions for a long period of time.
target_text: Na lomabibi e kena ibalebale ni da tao tu ena veiyalo bibi ena dua na gauna balavu.

source_text: Na lomabibi e kena ibalebale ni da tao tu ena veiyalo bibi ena dua na gauna balavu.
target_text: Depression is feeling stuck with heavy emotions for a long period of time.

source_text: Feeling depressed is not a sign of weakness.
target_text: Na lomabibi e sega ni kena ibalebale ni da malumalumu.

source_text: Na lomabibi e sega ni kena ibalebale ni da malumalumu.
target_text: Feeling depressed is not a sign of weakness.

source_text: With the right help, people who experience depression can get better.
target_text: Kevaka e soli na veivuke donu, era rawa ni sa bula vinaka tale o ira era lako curuma na lomabibi.

source_text: Kevaka e soli na veivuke donu, era rawa ni sa bula vinaka tale o ira era lako curuma na lomabibi.
target_text: With the right help, people who experience depression can get better.

source_text: We may feel unhappy most of the time and lose interest in things we usually enjoy.
target_text: E rawa ni da rarawa wasoma ka sega ni taleitaka na veika eda dau taleitaka e liu.

source_text: E rawa ni da rarawa wasoma ka sega ni taleitaka na veika eda dau taleitaka e liu.
target_text: We may feel unhappy most of the time and lose interest in things we usually enjoy.

source_text: We may feel tired most of the time and have little energy.
target_text: E rawa ni da dau oca wasoma ka sega ni levu na kaukauwa.

source_text: E rawa ni da dau oca wasoma ka sega ni levu na kaukauwa.
target_text: We may feel tired most of the time and have little energy.

source_text: We might notice changes in our appetite, such as eating too much or too little.
target_text: E rawa ni da raica na veisau ni noda kana me vaka na kana vakasivia se kana vakalailai.

source_text: E rawa ni da raica na veisau ni noda kana me vaka na kana vakasivia se kana vakalailai.
target_text: We might notice changes in our appetite, such as eating too much or too little.

source_text: We may have negative thoughts about ourselves and others.
target_text: E rawa ni tubu mai na nanuma ca me baleta na noda bula kei ira tale eso.

source_text: E rawa ni tubu mai na nanuma ca me baleta na noda bula kei ira tale eso.
target_text: We may have negative thoughts about ourselves and others.

source_text: We may have trouble sleeping and find it hard to get things done.
target_text: E rawa ni dredre na moce ka sega ni rawarawa meda qarava na veika eda dodonu me da cakava.

source_text: E rawa ni dredre na moce ka sega ni rawarawa meda qarava na veika eda dodonu me da cakava.
target_text: We may have trouble sleeping and find it hard to get things done.

source_text: Eating well, sleeping well and being active can improve our mood and wellbeing.
target_text: Na kana vakavinaka, moce vinaka kei na dau vakaukauwataki ni yagoda e rawa ni vakavinakataka na noda yalo kei na bula raraba.

source_text: Na kana vakavinaka, moce vinaka kei na dau vakaukauwataki ni yagoda e rawa ni vakavinakataka na noda yalo kei na bula raraba.
target_text: Eating well, sleeping well and being active can improve our mood and wellbeing.

source_text: Avoiding alcohol and other drugs helps us think clearly about our problems.
target_text: Na kena tarovi na gunu yaqona kei na wai gaga ni veivakamatenitaki e vukea na noda vakasama me rairai vinaka kina na sala ni wali ni leqa.

source_text: Na kena tarovi na gunu yaqona kei na wai gaga ni veivakamatenitaki e vukea na noda vakasama me rairai vinaka kina na sala ni wali ni leqa.
target_text: Avoiding alcohol and other drugs helps us think clearly about our problems.

source_text: Talking with people we trust can help us feel less alone.
target_text: Na veitalanoa kei ira na tamata eda nuitaka e rawa ni vakalailaitaka na noda galili.

source_text: Na veitalanoa kei ira na tamata eda nuitaka e rawa ni vakalailaitaka na noda galili.
target_text: Talking with people we trust can help us feel less alone.

source_text: If you have thoughts of harming yourself, seek professional help immediately.
target_text: Kevaka o nanuma mo vakaleqai iko, kerea vakatotolo na veivuke mai vei ira na kenadau.

source_text: Kevaka o nanuma mo vakaleqai iko, kerea vakatotolo na veivuke mai vei ira na kenadau.
target_text: If you have thoughts of harming yourself, seek professional help immediately.
